ignoreNone:  Ignore 'None' samples of the input signals. 
* Ignore none samples
* Ignore samples with missing members 

hideIdentical: Check to hide sequence of identical samples.
* Only write to output if the value has changed.
* Only add a struct member if the member value has changed.
* In case of struct/continuous, add an empty sample if no change.

KeepTags: The output samples shall keep the tag information of each input sample.

keepAttachments: Check to keep labels and relations of each input sample.

keepGroups: Check to keep the group information (e.g. transactions) of each input sample.